{"tid":664434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一見鍾情倒追約會男 美國婦瘋傳6.5萬短訊求愛","createTime":"2018-05-14T05:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e44fc0ba0f70f8e39cccc2e6ce14101676d8fe31","tid":664434,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】美國一名女子早前與一位男士約會見面，沒想到她對男方一見鍾情不能自拔，瘋狂傳了65000封短訊給對方，最終求愛不成反被告威脅、跟蹤和騷擾等重罪。<br />\n<br />\n31歲的艾德斯 (Jacqueline Ades) 周二於鳳凰城被警方拘捕，罪及涉及跟蹤、威脅和騷擾等。事緣她在去年1月於約會網站上面認識了一名男士，兩人相約見面吃飯，但她瘋狂愛上了對方，於是展開熱烈的追求。<br />\n<br />\n受害男指，艾德斯每日瘋狂傳短訊給他，平均一天高達500封，累計高達6.5萬封，內容包含，「你覺得我該拿你的血做些什麼事呢？我想要整個泡在裡面」、「你可以做你想做的事，但休想離開我，我會殺了你，我不想當殺人犯」。<br />\n<br />\n在4月時，受害男透過家中的閉路電視畫面發現，艾德斯闖入他的家中並在浴缸裡泡澡。立即報警，警方在艾德斯車上發現一把長刀，將她拘捕依照擅闖私人財產起訴。但艾德斯並沒有上庭應6訊，警方向她發出拘捕令，在上周她去到受害男的公司聲稱是對方的妻子而被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n在拘留期間，艾德斯向警方聲稱，自己沒有要傷害對方，只是因為真的很愛他，覺得對方是她的「靈魂伴侶」、「治癒天使」，不想要離開而已。當被問到是否覺得傳6萬多封的短訊太誇張時，她表示，「愛本來就是一件很誇張的事」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WkvoWMDslSDbyN2ikWh21A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-05-14/88816690-571d-11e8-a5c2-cf7db53ffd91_TEPHONE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWkvoWMDslSDbyN2ikWh21A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-05-14%2F88816690-571d-11e8-a5c2-cf7db53ffd91_TEPHONE.jpg&h=1402132b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A6%8B%E9%8D%BE%E6%83%85%E5%80%92%E8%BF%BD%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83%E7%94%B7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A9%A6%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B36-5%E8%90%AC%E7%9F%AD%E8%A8%8A%E6%B1%82%E6%84%9B-122000577.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%2580%2592%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B36-5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%25B1%2582%25E6%2584%259B-122000577.html&d=fq0aq0RQIHg2u0X0ok2fbtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=371d7a85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A6%8B%E9%8D%BE%E6%83%85%E5%80%92%E8%BF%BD%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%83%E7%94%B7-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A9%A6%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B36-5%E8%90%AC%E7%9F%AD%E8%A8%8A%E6%B1%82%E6%84%9B-122000577.html</a>"},{"pid":"aa2909203e4b6f31716a352ff525d517e76cfa63","tid":664434,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:38:32.000Z","msg":"怕"},{"pid":"b4c5f822550e9a350c22572a17a1eca8e631549c","tid":664434,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d214953a96d928087e43328a0ea1a13038e404c1","tid":664434,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:39:41.000Z","msg":"痴線有樣睇"},{"pid":"edfbe9aed4e6e28bc74ed49f0f89d7e90964b03e","tid":664434,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"快點來..."},{"pid":"62b19f39987a9f5d0e8054eaabde6532ad8204ea","tid":664434,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"係咪邊際性人格"}]}